{"tid":1334698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【亞視舊片廠炸藥案】辯方質疑警方事後召開記者會發放誤導訊息","createTime":"2019-07-20T08:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T08:18:29.000Z","uid":35790,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57585ecf32c50c288cbaff7e2d006236cbf32269","tid":1334698,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:01:39.000Z","msg":"&lt;回帶&gt;<br />\n【片廠炸藥案】辯方質疑警方事後召開記者會發放誤導訊息<br />\n<br />\n2017-10-26<br />\n<br />\n警方於前年6月在西貢蠔涌亞視舊片廠發現炸藥庫，5名男子被控串謀製造炸藥及管有炸藥共5項罪。案件於高院審理，控方今已完成傳召最後一名控方證人作供。<br />\n<br />\n控方最後一個證人為時任有組織罪案及三合會調查科高級督察王振業，第三被告彭艾烈的大狀盤問王時，質疑警方於拘捕被告後召開記者會，會上警方向傳媒提供的資料失實、誤導、對被告不公道。<br />\n<br />\n辯方舉例指，當日警方向傳媒展示撿獲的槍只是玩具槍，被告也從未被控管有非法武器罪，但警方從無向外澄清；警方在會上稱檢獲TATP製成品，但實情並非如此。<br />\n<br />\n王振業先是被問身為案件主管，當天有否出席記者會，王稱事後有看報紙，但記不起有否出席記者會，辯方質疑王説不記得只是講大話；對於玩具槍的事，王則表示他事後已調職，不知被告被控的罪名，<span style=\"color: red;\">而他承認開記者會時已就撿獲的化學品進行初步化驗，確認現場並沒有撿獲TATP，只是可製成TATP的化學混合物。</span><br />\n<br />\n辯方又稱當日主持記者會的三位警員中，有一位近日遭廉署起訴。但控方反對此提問，法官亦謂不合宜，辯方遂不再問。<br />\n<br />\n5被告依次為陳耀成（35歲）、鄭偉成（30歲）、彭艾烈（22歲）、胡啟賦（22歲）及文廷洛（24歲），他們否認串謀製造炸藥及管有炸藥等5罪。案件明天繼續。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171026/57378905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171026%2F57378905&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbhs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=0ff5bbad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171026%2F57378905&h=1b3a3283\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171026/57378905</a>"},{"pid":"7f531d4676c50ffa4133101ebd2cbca58c1ca27a","tid":1334698,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dd1b4ce259111bfb9034a1ad8ab5ffadce6a3d","tid":1334698,"uid":13467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:03:29.000Z","msg":"高調拉人<br />\n低調放人"},{"pid":"0ad6f54b69cc3312731e38b50edd3a9daf170a06","tid":1334698,"uid":72795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:05:04.000Z","msg":"全香港都係巨型軍火庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周圍都係氧氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a7325a4535ab39a0f6ca1e09cfb621084d6af3","tid":1334698,"uid":32485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記者會都唔記得 <br />\n會唔會連拉左人都唔記得?"},{"pid":"ecd5f8cc6967fb18645b56e03e2933451c7f6121","tid":1334698,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}